title: IAA Tonight | Are the Eagles and Bills the Two Best Teams In the NFL?
description: LeSean McCoy, Leger Douzable, Brandon Flowers and Auntie Chantel Tremertiere discuss the action from Monday Night Football, and whether the Eagles and Bills are the two best teams in their respective conferences after dominant wins over the Vikings and Titans. Plus, Auntie's Steelers are looking suspect after the first two games of the season. Will this be the first losing season for Mike Tomlin?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, LeSean McCoy, Chantel Tremetiere, Brandon Flowers)
